title: Will big name QBs stay or go?
itunes:title: Will big name QBs stay or go?
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal – discuss all the latest news from around the NFL, including the Broncos putting Brock Osweiler’s contract talks on hold out of respect for Peyton Manning, and Dolphins owner Stephen Ross saying he wants head coach Adam Gase to be the next Bill Belichick. Then, the heroes break down which players they think will get a franchise tag in 2016, and which quarterbacks could be looking for a new home next season.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
